title: "Per-query hybrid weight override: pm search --semantic-weight (post-v0.1)"
description: PRD line 1680 defers broader hybrid tuning; hybrid_semantic_weight is global-only. A per-query --semantic-weight lets agents bias keyword-heavy (exact IDs) vs concept-heavy queries.
